parse.title: University of Wisconsin Tolkien and Fantasy Society

wikitext.*:
'''University of Wisconsin Tolkien and Fantasy Society''' is a Tolkien society founded in September [[1966]] under the name The Tolkien Society at the University of Wisconsin-Madison. The name was changed in January 2001. The society publishes the journal ''[[Orcrist (journal)|Orcrist'']].
